{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/imate","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"imate"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Identity Design for Department of Information Culture","author":"Minkyoung Lee, U-infraway, Inseok Park, Hyuk Bae","date":"March 4th, 2013","hero_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.8472906403940887,"src":"/static/c1556a972e693061e0ab8b34c2fa2707/398d8/imate-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/c1556a972e693061e0ab8b34c2fa2707/8def4/imate-1.jpg 375w,\n/static/c1556a972e693061e0ab8b34c2fa2707/35c3d/imate-1.jpg 750w,\n/static/c1556a972e693061e0ab8b34c2fa2707/398d8/imate-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/c1556a972e693061e0ab8b34c2fa2707/b611c/imate-1.jpg 2126w","sizes":"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"}}}},"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.599999999999994%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"imate sketch 1\"\n        title=\"imate sketch 1\"\n        src=\"/static/1d541d6aa3dd0c51caac45aed2da2170/a2510/imate-sketch-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d541d6aa3dd0c51caac45aed2da2170/0479a/imate-sketch-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/1d541d6aa3dd0c51caac45aed2da2170/41099/imate-sketch-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/1d541d6aa3dd0c51caac45aed2da2170/a2510/imate-sketch-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/1d541d6aa3dd0c51caac45aed2da2170/f279f/imate-sketch-1.jpg 1121w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We designed a smart mannequin that recognizes human behavior and imitates it. Each mannequin character was assigned according to its use, and the user scenario and persona were created accordingly. There are four different types (two females, two males), Marianne, Di Panni, Endrani and Marianne (children's type). </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"imate 2\"\n        title=\"imate 2\"\n        src=\"/static/409bc5aa0545cfe8366c5da7868fe437/a2510/imate-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/409bc5aa0545cfe8366c5da7868fe437/0479a/imate-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/409bc5aa0545cfe8366c5da7868fe437/41099/imate-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/409bc5aa0545cfe8366c5da7868fe437/a2510/imate-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/409bc5aa0545cfe8366c5da7868fe437/58b23/imate-2.jpg 1417w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>While people can grasp the overall impression of their clothes through conventional mannequins, it is hard to know how they look like when they move in that clothes, and whether they are comfortable when they move in that suit. We wanted to show how clothes can be changed and used by creating mannequins that recognize and imitate the behavior of users. Therefore, we produced various types of mannequins to cover a range of users, ranging from men to women and children.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"imate type 1\"\n        title=\"imate type 1\"\n        src=\"/static/8367e9ba5e78e348f156ad0d5e5e8b29/a2510/imate-type-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8367e9ba5e78e348f156ad0d5e5e8b29/0479a/imate-type-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/8367e9ba5e78e348f156ad0d5e5e8b29/41099/imate-type-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/8367e9ba5e78e348f156ad0d5e5e8b29/a2510/imate-type-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/8367e9ba5e78e348f156ad0d5e5e8b29/c58a3/imate-type-1.jpg 1500w,\n/static/8367e9ba5e78e348f156ad0d5e5e8b29/3acf0/imate-type-1.jpg 2000w,\n/static/8367e9ba5e78e348f156ad0d5e5e8b29/0d91c/imate-type-1.jpg 3003w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Marian (male type)<br>\n· Height 180cm<br>\n· Male Mannequin Model for dynamic Image and masculine appearance<br>\n· Available to twist and move Head, arm, and waist<br>\n· Voice expression function</p>\n<p>Depani (female type)<br>\n· Height 170cm\n· Female mannequin model to express refined and feminine appearance\n· Available to twist and move Head, arm, and waist<br>\n· Voice expression function and multi-freedom robot hand can be mounted</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"imate type 2\"\n        title=\"imate type 2\"\n        src=\"/static/a33e735d1fcac895c2512071e4acfc37/a2510/imate-type-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a33e735d1fcac895c2512071e4acfc37/0479a/imate-type-2.jpg 250w,\n/static/a33e735d1fcac895c2512071e4acfc37/41099/imate-type-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/a33e735d1fcac895c2512071e4acfc37/a2510/imate-type-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/a33e735d1fcac895c2512071e4acfc37/c58a3/imate-type-2.jpg 1500w,\n/static/a33e735d1fcac895c2512071e4acfc37/3acf0/imate-type-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/a33e735d1fcac895c2512071e4acfc37/0d91c/imate-type-2.jpg 3003w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Endrani (female torso type)<br>\n· Height 70cm<br>\n· Female mannequin model to express refined and feminine appearance<br>\n· Available to twist and move Head, arm, and waist<br>\n· Torso body type for long dress</p>\n<p>Marian (kid type)<br>\n· Height 110cm<br>\n· Child Mannequin Model for dynamic Image and small appearance<br>\n· Available to twist and move Head, arm, and waist<br>\n· Voice expression function</p>\n<iframe title=\"vimeo-player\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/500962914\" width=\"640\" height=\"359\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p>Client | U-infraway</p>\n<p>Responsibility | case research, exterior design, persona, concept design, user scenario</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"imate"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2458793903","3255264069"]}